w.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2jyrzg99yo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2jyrzg99yo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2jyrzg99yo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20House%20Help%20Knew%20His%20Attacker%2C%20Let%20Him%20In%2C%20Suspect%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan's%20attacker%20is%20suspected%20to%20be%20related%20to%20one%20of%20the%20house%20helps%2C%20who%20also%20gave%20him%20entry%20into%20the%20actor's%20home%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20police%20have%20said.%20This%20help%20is%20now%20being%20questioned%20as%20Mumbai%20Police%20tries%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20shocking%20attack%20on%20the%2054-year-old%20actor%20in%20one%20of%20the%20poshest%20areas%20of%20Maximum%20City%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20suffered%20six%20stab%20injuries%2C%20one%20of%20them%20near%20his%20spine%2C%20and%20has%20been%20operated%20upon%20at%20Lilavati%20Hospital.%20He%20is%20reportedly%20out%20of%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%2C%20left%20red-faced%20after%20the%20shock%20attack%20on%20the%20actor%20during%20a%20burglary%20attempt%2C%20has%20said%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BAn%20unidentified%20person%20intruded%20in%20the%20residence%20of%20Actor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan.%20The%20actor%20and%20the%20intruder%20had%20a%20scuffle.%20The%20actor%20is%20injured%20and%20is%20being%20treated.%20Investigation%20is%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20cameras%20at%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20home%20did%20not%20capture%20anyone%20entering%20the%20premises%20within%20two%20hours%20before%20the%20attack%2C%20meaning%20that%20whoever%20attacked%20the%20actor%20had%20entered%20the%20building%20earlier%20and%20had%20been%20waiting%20to%20strike.%20Police%20are%20scanning%20CCTV%20footage%20to%20identify%20the%20attacker%2C%20