ection%2Farticleshow%2F117284140.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117284140.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDaniel%20Chapo%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20Mozambique's%20president%20despite%20opposition%20leader%20Venancio%20Mondlane's%20vow%20to%20'paralyze'%20the%20country%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20election%20results.%20Over%20300%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20post-election%20unrest.%20The%20inauguration%2C%20attended%20by%20South%20African%20and%20Guinea-Bissau%20presidents%2C%20faced%20calls%20for%20stability%20and%20unity%20in%20Mozambique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmozambique-daniel-chapo-inaugurated-after-disputed-election%2Farticleshow%2F117284140.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmozambique-daniel-chapo-inaugurated-after-disputed-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F117284140.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmozambique-daniel-chapo-inaugurated-after-disputed-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F117284140.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20winding%20up%20its%20operations%3A%20Founder%20Nate%20Anderson%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737000441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-short-seller-hindenburg-winding-up-its-operations-founder-nate-anderson-125011600181_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plan%20has%20been%20to%20wind%20up%20after%20we%20finished%20the%20pipeline%20of%20ideas%20we%20were%20working%20on%2C%20said%20Nate%20Anderson%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-short-seller-hindenburg-winding-up-its-operations-founder-nate-anderson-125011600181_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hostage%20Exchange%20And%20More%3A%20What%20To%20Know%20About%203-Phase%20Gaza%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20outgoing%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20the%20successful%20negotiation%20of%20the%20Gaza%20ceasefire-for-hostages%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20which%20was%20months%20in%20the%20making%2C%20ending%20over%2015%20months%20of%20conflict.%20The%20agreed-upon%20deal%20is%20structured%20in%20three%20phases%2C%20including%20a%20complete%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20from%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20including%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20noted%20the%20final%20deal%2C%20which%20was%20helped%20across%20the%20line%20by%20an%20envoy%20of%20his%20successor%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20largely%20mirrored%20the%20framework%20of%20a%20proposal%20he%20made%20back%20in%20May.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20plan%20was%20developed%20and%20negotiated%20by%20my%20team%20and%20will%20be%20largely%20implemented%20by%20the%20incoming%20administration.%20That's%20why%20I%20told%20my%20team%20to%20keep%20the%20incoming%20administration%20fully%20informed%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20farewell%20address%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20from%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20Phase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20the%20details%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%20between%20the%20Palestine-based%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%2C%20Biden%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20deal%20is%20structured%20in%20three%20phases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20stage%20would%20last%20six%20weeks%20and%20see%20%26quot%3Ba%20full%20and%20complete%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%2C%20Biden%20said%20announcing%20the%20ceasefire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20noted%20that%20in%20this%20phase%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20number%20of%20hostages%26quot%3B%20held%20by%20Hamas%2C%20including%20women%2C%20the%20elderly%20and%20the%20sick%2C%20would%20be%20released%20in%20exchange%20for%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%20He%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20many%20hostages%20would%20be%20released%2C%20but%20Qatari%20Prime%20Minister%20Mohammed%20bin%20Abdulrahman%20bin%20Jassim%20Al%20Thani%20told%20reporters%20earlier%20that%20it%20would%20be%2033.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20BBC%20report%2C%20three%20hostages%20would%20be%20released%20straight%20away%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20exchange%20taking%20place%20over%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20the%20first%20six%20weeks%20after%20the%20agreement%20came%20into%20force%20on%20January%2019%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20would%20pull%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Ball%26quot%3B%20populated%20areas%20of%20Gaza%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Palestinians%20%5Bcould%5D%20also%20return%20to%20their%20neighbourhoods%20in%20all%20the%20areas%20of%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20ceasefire%20would%20persist%20%26quot%3Bas%20long%20as%20the%20negotiations%20continue%26quot%3B.%20There%20would%20also%20be%20a%20surge%20in%20humanitarian%20aid%20deliveries%20to%20Gaza%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20lorries%20allowed%20in%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Biden%2C%20a%20number%20of%20details%20need%20to%20be%20negotiated%20to%20move%20from%20the%20first%20phase%20to%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20but%20the%20plan%20says%20that%20if%20negotiations%20take%20longer%20than%20six%20weeks%2C%20the%20ceasefire%20will%20continue%20as%20long%20as%20the%20negotiations%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20Gaza's%202.3%20million%20population%20has%20been%20displaced%20because%20of%20Israeli%20evacuation%20orders%2C%20Israeli%20strikes%20and%20fighting%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%20Phase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Biden%2C%20phase%20two%20of%20the%20deal%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20will%20see%20the%20release%20of%20remaining%20living%20hostages%2C%20including%20men%2C%20in%20return%20for%20more%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20all%20remaining%20Israeli%20forces%20will%20be%20withdrawn%20from%20Gaza%20and%20the%20temporary%20ceasefire%20will%20become%20permanent%2C%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Palestinian%20officials%20said%20detailed%20negotiations%20for%20the%20second%20and%20third%20stages%20would%20begin%20on%20the%2016th%20day%20of%20the%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20had%20seized%20251%20hostages%20when%20it%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%20It%20is%20reportedly%20still%20holding%2094%20captives%2C%20although%20Israel%20believes%20that%20only%2060%20are%20still%20alive.%20Meanwhile%2C%C2%A0Israel%20is%20likely%20to%20release%20about%201%2C000%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20in%20return%20for%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%20Phase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20deal%20would%20involve%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20Gaza%2C%20something%20which%20could%20take%20years%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20any%20remaining%20hostages'%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20finally%20Phase%203%20--%20any%20final%20remains%20of%20hostages%20who%20have%20been%20killed%20will%20be%20returned%20to%20their%20families%20and%20a%20major%20reconstruction%20plan%20for%20Gaza%20will%20begin%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20followed%20the%20negotiations%20can%20attest%20that%20the%20road%20to%20this%20deal%20has%20not%20been%20easy.%20I%20have%20worked%20in%20foreign%20policy%20for%20decades.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20negotiations%20that%20I%20have%20ever%20experienced.%20I%20have%20reached%20this%20point%20because%20of%20the%20pressure%20that%20Israel%20built%20on%20Hamas%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737000360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F3u0cqpj8_gaza-hostage-deal-afp_625x300_16_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhostage-exchange-and-more-what-to-know-about-3-phase-gaza-deal-7484274%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20outgoing%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20the%20successful%20negotiation%20of%20the%20Gaza%20ceasefire-for-hostages%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20which%20was%20months%20in%20the%20making%2C%20ending%20over%2015%20months%20of%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhostage-exchange-and-more-what-to-know-about-3-phase-gaza-deal-7484274%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20has%20been%20stockpiling%20a%20key%20US%20crop%20before%20Trump%20takes%20office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22farming%20soybeans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5383bd37eab8eaaa1c61d097%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUeslei%20Marcelino%2FBrazil%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20is%20loading%20up%20on%20soybeans%20amid%20US%20trade%20war%20fears.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20soybean%20imports%20rose%206.5%25%20in%202024%2C%20hedging%20against%20potential%20Trump%20trade%20policies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIntensifying%20US-China%20trade%20tensions%20could%20hit%20the%20soybean%20trade%2C%20impacting%20US%20farmers%20and%20rural%20economies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20stockpiling%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-imports-trade-war-biden-tariffs-chips-demand-economy-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemiconductor%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20its%20trade%20war%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20China%20imported%20a%20record%20105.03%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20soybeans%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20crop%20that%20was%20embroiled%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20war%20with%20China%20during%20his%20first%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20import%20of%20US%20soybeans%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20also%20spiked%20last%20year%2C%20rising%206.5%25%20from%202023%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fview-chinas-december-export-growth-gathers-pace-imports-recover-2025-01-13%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters'%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0calculations%20of%20official%20customs%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuyers%20from%20China%20%E2%80%94%20the%20world's%20largest%20soybean%20consumers%20%E2%80%94%20were%20likely%20stocking%20up%20on%20the%20crop%20to%20hedge%20any%20geopolitical%20risks%20ahead%20of%20Trump's%20second%20term%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20threatened%20to%20put%2060%25%20tariffs%20on%20all%20Chinese%20goods%20during%20his%20second%20presidential%20term%2C%20igniting%20fears%20of%20an%20intensification%20in%20trade%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20US%20ramps%20up%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports%2C%20China%20could%20target%20US%20agricultural%20imports%20as%20retaliatory%20tariff%20countermeasures%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajiv%20Biswas%2C%20an%20international%20economist%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BAsian%20Megatrends%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20soybean%20imports%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20key%20target%20for%20China's%20retaliatory%20tariff%20measures%20due%20to%20the%20very%20large%20scale%20of%20China's%20soybean%20imports%20from%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222134e546-f485-416e-bc49-5732c0f219b1%5C%22%3EThe%20power%20of%20the%20soybean%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20soybean%20producer%20after%20Brazil.%20It%20accounts%20for%20about%20a%20quarter%20of%20China's%20import%20of%20the%20oilseed%2C%20which%20it%20typically%20uses%20for%20animal%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20term%20as%20president%2C%20Trump%20slapped%20heavy%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20China%20imposed%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20US%20agricultural%20produce%2C%20including%20soybeans%2C%20sending%20American%20soybean%20exports%20to%20China%20sharply%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20on%20some%20of%20these%20farm%20imports%20were%20waived%20ahead%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-buying-more-american-soybeans-ahead-of-trade-war-talks-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS-China%20trade%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f74853b-bd2b-4508-b201-d9ad6059d2a0%5C%22%3EImpact%20on%20American%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20replay%20of%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20during%20Trump's%20second%20presidency%20could%20hit%20US%20soybean%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20scenario%20where%20China%20imposes%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20on%20US%20soybeans%20in%202025%2C%20the%20impact%20would%20again%20likely%20be%20a%20substantial%20economic%20loss%20for%20the%20US%20soybean%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Biswas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20from%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsoygrowers.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fanalysis-shows-tariff-induced-trade-war-would-hurt-u-s-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Soybean%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20the%20National%20Corn%20Growers%20Association%20shows%20that%20a%20new%20trade%20war%20would%20result%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20drop%20in%20corn%20and%20soy%20exports%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20tons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrazil%20and%20Argentina%20would%20claim%20the%20lost%20market%20share%2C%20which%20would%20be%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20American%20growers%20to%20reclaim%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20two%20associations%20said%20in%20October%2C%20cautioning%20against%20a%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20isn't%20enough%20demand%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20to%20offset%20a%20major%20loss%20of%20soybean%20exports%20to%20China%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20trade%20war%20would%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bripple%20impact%20across%20the%20US%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20economies%20where%20farmers%20live%2C%20purchase%20inputs%2C%20use%20farm%20and%20personal%20services%2C%20and%20purchase%20household%20goods%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20two%20agriculture%20trade%20associations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20is%2C%20Chinese%20soybean%20importers%20have%20diversified%20their%20sources%20since%20Trump's%20first%20presidential%20term%2C%20with%20Brazil%20a%20major%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20decline%20in%20Chinese%20soybean%20demand%20%E2%80%94%20made%20worse%20by%20the%20country's%20ongoing%20economic%20downturn%20%E2%80%94%20would%20also%20weigh%20on%20the%20trade%20in%20a%20well-supplied%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20a%20Trump%20presidency%20could%20reignite%20US-Mainland%20China%20trade%20tensions%20and%20potential%20Chinese%20tariffs%20on%20US%20soybean%20exports%2C%20we%20anticipate%20that%20the%20expected%20decline%20in%20Chinese%20demand%20will%20mitigate%20price%20impacts%2C%26quot%3B%20BMI%20Research%20wrote%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elast%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-soybean-imports-us-trump-trade-tariff-war-agriculture-farmers-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%