jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20bought%20LinkedIn%20in%202016%20for%20%2426.2%20billion%20in%20cash.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Satya%20Nadella%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20social%20network%20would%20complement%20Microsoft's%20business-focused%20software%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-office-365%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20Office%20365%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20suite%20of%20productivity%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20tech%20companies%2C%20LinkedIn%20has%20had%20its%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20post-pandemic%20years.%20LinkedIn%20Premium%20earned%20%241.7%20billion%20from%20subscribers%20in%202023%2C%20executives%20revealed%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20call.%20However%2C%20the%20job%20cuts%20that%20have%20plagued%20the%20tech%20industry%20didn't%20spare%20the%20networking%20site%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-linkedin-culture-ai-pips-layoffs-perks-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20laid%20off%20hundreds%20of%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20financial%20turbulence%20at%20the%20company%2C%20LinkedIn%20is%20still%20a%20valuable%20networking%20site%20used%20by%20millions%20of%20people%20and%20companies%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20Here's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20using%20the%20platform%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22832522f3-7419-4cc6-ac5c-195eb37038fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinkedIn%20essentials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20professional%20focus%2C%20LinkedIn%20is%20quite%20similar%20to%20social%20networking%20sites%20like%20Facebook.%20It's%20based%20on%20principles%20like%20connecting%20to%20friends%20(or%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20LinkedIn%2C%20%26quot%3Bconnections%2C%26quot%3B)%2C%20posting%20updates%2C%20sharing%20and%20liking%20content%2C%20and%20messaging%20other%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20also%20puts%20a%20professional%20spin%20on%20ideas%20you%20know%20from%20Facebook.%20Your%20profile%2C%20for%20example%2C%20becomes%20a%20resume%2C%20complete%20with%20work%20experience%2C%20accomplishments%2C%20recommendations%2C%20and%20referrals%20from%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20also%20offers%20things%20you%20won't%20find%20in%20other%20places%2C%20like%20a%20full-featured%20career%20board%2C%20where%20you%20can%20search%20for%20and%20apply%20for%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20employment%20services%20are%20now%20compatible%20with%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20when%20applying%20for%20a%20position%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-share-linkedin-profile%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshare%20your%20LinkedIn%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sometimes%20means%20you%20won't%20need%20to%20painstakingly%20enter%20your%20work%20experience%20into%20a%20long%20online%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20new%20to%20LinkedIn%2C%20here's%20a%20quick%20tour%20around%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22237739e4-ed7e-4b32-ad89-f1b04826533d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20quick%20tour%20of%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20akin%20to%20Facebook's%20news%20feed.%20Here%20you%20can%20see%20posts%20made%20by%20other%20LinkedIn%20users%2C%20and%20make%20your%20own%20posts%20that%20others%20can%20see%2C%20like%2C%20share%2C%20and%20comment%20on.%20Like%20Facebook%2C%20you%20can%20limit%20your%20posts%20to%20just%20connections%20in%20your%20network%2C%20or%20share%20your%20thoughts%20with%20everyone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20Network%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20where%20you%20can%20see%20your%20existing%20network%20of%20connections%2C%20and%20search%20for%20LinkedIn%20users%20to%20invite%20to%20join%20your%20network.%20You%20can%20also%20see%20existing%20invitations%20you've%20received%20from%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20career%20site.%20You%20can%20search%20for%20and%20apply%20for%20jobs%2C%20get%20information%20about%20companies%20you're%20interested%20in%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20You%20can%20set%20up%20notifications%20and%20get%20emails%20when%20there%20are%20new%20job%20postings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMessaging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20leads%20to%20an%20instant%20messaging%20platform%20you%20can%20use%20to%20chat%20with%20people%20in%20your%20network.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20it%20to%20send%20messages%20to%20people%20outside%20your%20network%20with%20something%20called%20InMail%2C%20if%20you%20subscribe%20to%20certain%20tiers%20of%20LinkedIn%20Premium.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20where%20you%20can%20find%20your%20profile%2C%20which%20is%20akin%20to%20your%20resume.%20Here%2C%20you%20can%20show%20your%20career%20history%20by%20posting%20your%20work%20experience%2C%20accomplishments%2C%20education%2C%20current%20location%2C%20and%20more.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20LinkedIn%20account%2C%20this%20should%20be%20as%20polished%20as%20your%20actual%20resume%2C%20as%20you%20can%20expect%20professional%20connections%20and%20recruiters%20to%20look%20at%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e140118b-b055-4ddf-bec9-43717947345e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20you%20can%20do%20with%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20clear%20that%20LinkedIn%20is%20a%20tool%20you%20can%20use%20to%20enhance%20your%20professional%20networking%20and%20job%20searching%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20use%20the%20site%20to%20grow%20their%20contacts%20and%20find%20career%20opportunities%2C%20and%20the%20Jobs%20section%20of%20the%20site%20is%20a%20powerful%20tool%20for%20finding%20and%20applying%20for%20jobs.%20There%20are%20settings%20on%20LinkedIn%20that%20let%20you%20alert%20recruiters%20that%20you're%20actively%20job%20searching%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20use%20LinkedIn%20to%20enhance%20their%20professional%20reputation%20by%20making%20posts%20in%20the%20news%20feed%2C%20and%20commenting%20on%20other%20people's%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20other%20tech%20companies%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Microsoft%20and%20its%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-copilot-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20tool%20%E2%80%94%20LinkedIn%20has%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20AI%20products.%20LinkedIn%20has%20unveiled%20its%20own%20AI-powered%20writing%20assistant%20that%20can%20generate%20personalized%20suggestions%20for%20your%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4d0e50c-c1df-4d4d-b442-79d1e72debff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinkedIn%20Premium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20Premium%20is%20a%20subscription%20version%20of%20LinkedIn%20that%20adds%20a%20number%20of%20additional%20features%2C%20such%20as%20online%20professional%20development%20classes%2C%20insights%20into%20who's%20viewing%20your%20profile%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20instant%20message%20anyone%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20not%20in%20your%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20Premium%20offers%20four%20types%20of%20plans%20with%20different%20price%20points%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20needs.%20Premium%20Career%20is%20for%20professionals%20and%20job-seekers%20looking%20to%20further%20their%20careers%2C%20while%20Premium%20Business%2C%20Sales%20Navigator%2C%20and%20Recruiter%20Lite%20are%20for%20employers%2C%20businesses%2C%20or%20sales%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20plan%2C%20LinkedIn%20Premium%20Career%2C%20costs%20%2439.99%20for%20one%20month%2C%20or%20you%20can%20purchase%20an%20annual%20package