0the%20drug%20GHB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalfway%20through%20Wednesday's%20hearing%2C%20which%20the%20brothers%20did%20not%20attend%2C%20Paul%20mentioned%20that%20key%20prosecution%20evidence%20%E2%80%94%20the%202009%20video.%20She%20criticized%20its%20probative%20value%2C%20telling%20the%20judge%20it%20%26quot%3Bshows%20the%20lack%20of%20force%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20consensual%20sexual%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20view%2C%20having%20sex%20with%20a%20woman%20who%20is%20physically%20incapacitated%20is%20basically%20rape%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20responded%2C%20citing%20the%20prosecution's%20description%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20asked%20prosecutor%20Andrew%20Jones%20to%20describe%20the%20video%20more%20fully%2C%20which%20he%20then%20did%20publicly%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btrophy%26quot%3B%20tape%20that%20the%20government%20had%20seized%20as%20evidence%2C%20and%20said%20it%20depicts%20one%20of%20the%20twins%20having%20sex%20with%20a%20woman%20he%20said%20the%20government%20has%20not%20spoken%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20the%20video%20shows%20Oren%20or%20Alon%2C%20but%20that%20as%20it%20begins%2C%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20these%20very%20stone-cold%20sober%20defendants%20sets%20up%20a%20tripod.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20bed.%20She's%20naked%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20tries%20to%20speak%2C%20it's%20incoherent.%20She%20is%20mumbling%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20appears%20unable%20to%20move%2C%20he%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20alleged%20rape%2C%20%26quot%3Bshe%20manages%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20but%20then%20collapses%20back%20on%20the%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosecutor%20said%20the%20video%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20video%20was%20mentioned%20again%20by%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Oren%20Alexander%2C%20Richard%20Klugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20referred%20to%20the%20woman%20in%20the%20video%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20sexual%20partner%26quot%3B%20of%20either%20of%20the%20twins%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20woman%20who%20stood%20up%20immediately%20after%20having%20sex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20prosecutors%20are%20misrepresenting%20evidence%20when%20they%20say%20the%20woman%20was%20unable%20to%20speak%2C%20given%20that%20%26quot%3Bshe%20was%20mumbling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20call%20someone%20incapacitated%20who%20is%20able%20to%20stand%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20%E2%80%94%20at%20which%20point%20the%20judge%20called%20his%20assessment%20%26quot%3Bnonsense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20Caproni%20rejected%20defense%20arguments%20that%20the%20siblings%20were%20neither%20a%20danger%20to%20the%20community%20nor%20a%20flight%20risk%2C%20and%20that%2C%20as%20Klugh%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20been%20no%20more%20orgying.%20They're%20married.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20turned%20down%20a%20%24115%20million%20bail%20package%20and%20a%20promise%20that%20the%20three%20would%20live%20together%20in%20Florida%20on%20home%20confinement.%20The%20home%20would%20have%20an%20in-house%20security%20team%2C%20window%20sensors%2C%20and%20an%20alarm%20system%2C%20the%20defense%20lawyers%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaproni%20said%20her%20denial%20was%20based%20in%20large%20part%20on%20federal%20appellate%20case%20law%20from%20New%20York's%20Second%20Circuit%20that%20bars%20judges%20from%20accepting%20a%20two-tiered%20bail%20system%20where%20only%20wealthy%20defendants%20can%20spend%20money%20for%2024-hour%20monitoring%20by%20an%20in-house%20security%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20real%20problems%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Second%20Circuit%2C%20if%20the%20only%20way%20I%20can%20mitigate%20danger%20to%20the%20community%20is%20to%20create%20a%20private%20jail%2C%20then%20I%20can't%2