e%20code%2C%20Kean's%20software%20controls%20limited%20steering%20and%20acceleration.%20It's%20nothing%20that%20EV%20makers%20like%20Tesla%20aren't%20already%20selling%2C%20but%20he%20and%20his%20buddies%20custom-engineered%20their%20product%2C%20made%20with%20Chinese%20phone%20parts%2C%20for%20Malaysia's%20national%20auto%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20pitch%20is%20that%20for%20%24800%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20%2410%2C000%20hatchback%20can%20plug%20in%20Kean's%20dashcam%20via%20two%20cables%20and%20get%20partial%20self-driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20driver%20using%20Kommu's%20dashcam%20sits%20as%20his%20car%20cruises%20on%20its%20own%20down%20a%20highway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6729a35788cea3ba1c1e43ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKean%20Wei%20Wong%20and%20his%20buddies%20are%20selling%20a%20dashcam%20they've%20custom-engineered%20to%20work%20in%20Malaysia's%20cheaper%20cars.%3Cp%3EKommu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKean%20is%20unsure%20if%20their%20product%20is%20legal%2C%20though%20he%20said%20they%20haven't%20seen%20trouble%20from%20authorities%20and%20secured%20prize%20money%20from%20a%20government-affiliated%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20gray%20area.%20Malaysia%20isn't%20a%20very%20regulated%20country%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20there%20are%20opportunities%20for%20startups%20like%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247ebe855-e0ec-4f86-a7da-bce6c29f549d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOff%20to%20a%20good%20start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20political%20reckoning%20saw%20Malaysia%20cycle%20through%20five%20prime%20ministers%20in%20six%20years%2C%20until%20Anwar%20Ibrahim%2C%20the%20current%20prime%20minister%2C%20squeezed%20through%20the%20November%202022%20national%20polls%20through%20a%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20