%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2427.6%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20all%20local%20ventures%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225189%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Malaysia's%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Anwar%20Ibrahim%2C%20delivers%20a%20speech%20during%20the%20groundbreaking%20ceremony%20for%20Malaysia's%20first%20Google%20data%20center%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674805edfa0140cdd5661162%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223461%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnwar%20has%20been%20announcing%20new%20data%20center%20deals%20and%20pushing%20out%20financial%20incentives%20for%20startups%20to%20settle%20down%20in%20Malaysia.%3Cp%3EMOHD%20RASFAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20different.%20Because%20this%20time%2C%20the%20government%20isn't%20doing%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tan%20Eng%20Tong%2C%20a%20startup%20advisor%20who%20runs%20an%20education%20center%20for%20tech%20workers%20in%20Malaysia.%20He%20spent%20the%201990s%20building%20his%20career%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20with%20Seagate%20and%20Hewlett-Packard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20believes%20Malaysia's%20last%20tech%20mega-project%20in%20the%201990s%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20government%20trying%20to%20force%20a%20revolution.%20Then-Prime%20Minister%20Mahathir%20Mohamad%20cleared%20land%20for%20global%20companies%20to%20settle%20down%2C%20dreaming%20of%20transforming%20greater%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20into%20an%20IT%20powerhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20of%20the%20prized%20multinationals%20eventually%20used%20their%20new%20Malaysian%20bases%20for%20low-cost%20labor%20in%20manufacturing%20and%20outsourcing.%20When%20a%20BI%20reporter%20visited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabandoned-mall-cyberjaya-malaysia-silicon-valley-malakat-tiktok-2022-12%23as-cbd-perdana-3s-name-implies-its-one-of-three-similar-areas-when-i-checked-out-cbd-perdana-2-i-found-that-it-too-was-full-of-vacant-spaces-13%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECyberjaya%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20a%20development%20near%20the%20capital%20meant%20to%20house%20the%20world's%20hottest%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20largely%20residential%20area%20was%20filled%20with%20abandoned%20business%20hubs%20and%20quiet%20malls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Malaysia's%20then-Prime%20Minister%20Mahathir%20Mohamad%20speaks%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Cyberjaya%20in%202020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6729ddcb5ec9bfa3d63bb45d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECyberjaya%20had%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20project%20spearheaded%20by%20Mahathir%20Mohamad.%3Cp%3EXinhua%2FChong%20Voon%20Chung%20via%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba3bf6d5-dc4b-4f70-9f24-bd9e062d3df7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%2C000%20startups%20by%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20country%20is%20trying%20a%20new%20approach.%20Its%20semiconductor%20industry%2C%20largely%20based%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Penang%2C%20already%20houses%20Intel%20and%20Texas%20Instruments.%20Officials%20have%20announced%20a%20plan%20to%20bring%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmalaysia-pm-says-targeting-over-100-bln-investment-semiconductor-chips-2024-05-28%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20billion%20in%20additional%20investment%20for%20the%20sector%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20specifying%20a%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnwar%20is%20continuing%20the%20prior%20administration's%20goal%20of%20producing%205%2C000%20local%20startups%20and%20five%20unicorns%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Delivery%20drivers%20for%20delivery%20app%20Grab%20line%20up%20while%20waiting%20for%20deliveries%20outside%20a%20popular%20street%20food%20vendor%20in%20July%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6748085eede4eeae392a36ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrab%2C%20a%20Malaysian%20ride-hailing%20startup%20that%20moved%20to%20Singapore%2C%20has%20become%20Southeast%20Asia's%20version%20of%20Uber%20and%20is%20now%20Kuala%20Lumpur's%20poster%20child%20for%20unicorns.%3Cp%3EMatthews%20Hunt%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENorman%20Matthieu%20Vanhaecke%2C%20the%20Belgian-Malay%20CEO%20of%20Cradle%20Fund%2C%20the%20government's%20agency%20supporting%20early-stage%20firms%2C%20said%20the%20country%20now%20has%20about%204%2C000%20startups.%20The%20overwhelming%20majority%20are%20located%20in%20the%20capital%20and%20the%20state%20that%20surrounds%20it%2C%20Selangor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Vanhaecke%20says%20Malaysia's%20true%20near-term%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20on%20the%20map%20and%20have%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20join%20Tokyo%2C%20Seoul%2C%20and%20Singapore%20on%20global%20lists%20like%20Startup%20Genome's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstartupgenome.com%2Farticle%2Fglobal-startup-ecosystem-ranking-2023-top-30-plus-runners-up%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eecosystem%20ranking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingapore%20and%20Indonesia%20have%20enjoyed%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20venture%20capital%20activity%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%20In%202023%2C%20they%20secured%20651%20and%20165%20deals%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20investment%20database%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalaysia%20recorded%2071%20deals%20that%20year%2C%20and%20the%20total%20annual%20value%20of%20its%20deals%20has%20never%20reached%20%241%20billion%2C%20per%20PitchBook.%20The%20total%20value%20of%20deals%20in%20Singapore%20has%20eclipsed%20%249%20billion%20annually%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Malaysia%20Digital%20Economy%20Corporation%2C%20a%20government%20agency%20tasked%20with%20attracting%20tech%20investment%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20give%20foreign%20startups%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoft-landing%20zone%26quot%3B%20in%20Malaysia%20through%20coworking%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20told%20BI%20that%20since%202016%2C%20it%20has%20partnered%20with%2023%20locations%20that%20have%20serviced%20about%20600%20startups.%20These%20firms%20are%20promised%20low%20business%20costs%20and%20potential%20access%20to%20government%20and%20private%20sector%20financing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d437098-bcfe-42f9-b3c7-8b011851dd3d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMalaysia%20opens%20its%20state%20funds%20to%20startups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENoor%20Amy%20Ismail%2C%20an%20analyst%20asked%20by%20the%20Malaysian%20government%20to%20assess%20the%20local%20VC%20scene%20in%202023%2C%20said%20she%20studied%20South%20Korea's%202014%20tech%20drive%20for%20her%20recommendations.%20There%2C%20government%20funds%20set%20the%20stage%2C%20then%20petered%20off%20as%20private%20investors%20poured%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20advised%20Malaysian%20officials%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20what%20our%20venture%20capital%20road%20map%20is%20trying%20to%20address%2C%20to%20get%20more%20corporate%20investors%20on%20board%20to%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20and%20national%20funds%2C%20which%20have%20long%20dominated%20investing%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20have%20been%20opening%20their%20coffers%20to%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20founder%2C%20Jimmy%20How%2C%20said%20state%20executives%20were%20far%20more%20risk-averse%2010%20years%20ago%20when%20he%20started%20his%20affiliate%20marketing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20then%2C%20guys%20like%20Khazanah%20wouldn't%20even%20look%20at%20startups%20like%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20How%20said.%20Khazanah%2C%20Malaysia's%20main%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khazanah.com.my%2Fnews_press_releases%2Fkhazanah-launches-future-malaysia-programme-under-dana-impak-to-spur-the-local-start-up-ecosystem%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearmarked%20%241.3%20billion%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20startups%20and%20venture%20capital%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow's%20company%20received%20an%20investment%20from%20Penjana%20Kapital%2C%20a%20national%20venture%20program%2C%20during%20a%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGokula%20Krishnan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Vircle%2C%20a%20financial%20literacy%20app%20for%20kids%2C%20said%20his%20firm%20received%20a%20seed%20investment%20from%20Khazanah%20in%202023.%20It%20helped%20convince%20him%20to%20stay%20in%20Malaysia%20instead%20of%20leaving%20for%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalent%20is%20relatively%20cheap.%20Available%20office%20space%20is%20cheap.%20Cost%20of%20living%20is%20supercheap%2C%20even%20compared%20to%20Vietnam%20or%20Indonesia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20Malaysia.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20any%20other%20country%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%20that%20has%20this%20mix.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22820eb7cc-6e1c-4a30-b745-f0f05950aabc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20more%20'shit-hole%20state%20of%20mind'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKhailee%20Ng%2C%20an%20energetic%20Malaysian%20with%20a%20mane%20of%20black%20hair%20flowing%20down%20to%20his%20shoulders%2C%20is%20perhaps%20the%20biggest%20name%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur's%20venture%20capital%20scene.%20He's%20a%20managing%20partner%20with%20the%20US%20venture%20firm%20500%20Global%2C%20which%20has%20seeded%20at%20least%20six%20unicorns%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalaysia%2C%20burdened%20by%20a%20history%20of%20infighting%20and%20policy%20reversals%2C%20has%20for%20too%20long%20wallowed%20in%20a%20self-defeating%20attitude%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%26quot%3Bshit-hole%20state%20of%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20jogs%20at%20a%20park%20before%20the%20skyline%20of%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20in%20June%202018.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67480af4fa0140cdd566118e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222393%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENg%20said%20Malaysia%20has%20long%20endured%20a%20self-critical%20mindset%20that%20puts%20itself%20down.%3Cp%3EMOHD%20RASFAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ng%20said%20he's%20seen%20far%20less%20of%20that%20among%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20getting%20funding%2C%20they're%20kinda%20seeing%20that%20things%20are%20working.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20tech%20startups%20are%20starting%20to%20be%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20something%20good%20will%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20team%20analyzed%20198%20local%20startups%20from%20January%202023%20to%20June%202024%20and%20found%20that%2033%20were%20profitable%2C%20with%20at%20least%2020%25%20annual%20growth%20and%20%245%20million%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20that%20group%2C%2011%20had%20over%2060%25%20growth%20and%20%2410%20million%20in%20annual%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20shocked%2C%26quot%3B%20Ng%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20500%20Global%20has%20since%20invested%20in%20five%20of%20those%2011%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9ee3b8f-3485-40c9-9966-2270da4452ad%5C%22%3EStronger%20currency%20boosts%20purchasing%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Puchong%2C%20a%20town%20about%2010%20miles%20south%20of%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20entrepreneurs%20Amirul%20Merican%20and%20Chor%20Chee%20Hoe%20were%20preparing%20just%20after%20dawn%20to%20meet%20their%20startup's%20new%20landlord.%20They're%20looking%20to%20move%20into%20a%20factory%20to%20expand%20production%20at%20their%20firm%2C%20Qarbotech%2C%20by%20