6792d73b7%5C%22%3EQuelling%20the%20brain%20drain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Malaysia's%20long-term%20challenges%20is%20quelling%20a%20brain%20drain%20to%20Singapore%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201.1%20million%20Malaysians%20lived%20in%20Singapore%20in%202022%2C%20about%20three-quarters%20of%20whom%20were%20skilled%20or%20semi-skilled%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJayant%20Menon%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20who%20studies%20Asian%20trade%20and%20investment%20at%20the%20ISEAS-Yusof%20Ishak%20Institute%20in%20Singapore%2C%20said%20if%20Malaysia%20does%20not%20fix%20issues%20like%20its%20talent%20exodus%2C%20the%20tech%20push%20could%20become%20a%20collection%20of%20short-term%20investments%20spilling%20over%20from%20the%20US-China%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%2C%20the%20analyst%20asked%20to%20assess%20Malaysia's%20tech%20scene%2C%20said%20the%20government%20should%20work%20on%20bringing%20middle-class%20female%20talent%20back%20into%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2053%25%20of%20Malaysian%20STEM%20graduates%20in%202021%20were%20women%2C%20far%20higher%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undp.org%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpublications%2Fwomen-science-technology-engineering-and-mathematics-asia-pacific%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMarch%25206%252C%25202024%26amp%3Btext%3DRepresentation%2520of%2520women%2520in%2520STEM%2Cglobal%2520average%2520of%252029.3%2520percent.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20average%20of%2029%25.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20moment%20they%20enter%20the%20workforce%2C%20that%20number%20drops%20to%20about%2043%20to%2044%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Amy%20said%20of%20how%20many%20working%20STEM%20professionals%20are%20women.%20Middle-income%20Malaysians%20are%20often%20under%20pressure%20to%20care%20for%20both%20their%20children%20and%20retiring%20parents%2C%20and%20many%20women%20choose%20to%20take%20on%20that%20role%20since%20they%20earn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freema