9016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20more%20compelling%20than%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshikari%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(hunter)%20exploits%20is%20the%20story%20of%20his%20redemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilly%20Arjan%20recalls%20his%20forties%20as%20the%20last%20time%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20rifle.%20As%20he%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20finally%20stopped%20shooting%20in%201960%20when%20I%20was%20overcome%20with%20remorse%20for%20ending%20the%20life%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20beautiful%20leopard%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20headlights%20of%20my%20jeep.%20I%20had%20no%20right%20whatsoever%20to%20destroy%20what%20I%20could%20not%20create.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETapping%20on%20this%20sentiment%2C%20he%20gravitated%20to%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnknowst%20to%20many%2C%20this%20spur-of-the-moment%20decision%20went%20on%20to%20have%20an%20outsized%20impact%20on%20the%20future%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20wildlife%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20life%20dedicated%20to%20the%20tigers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20poignancy%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20Brinda%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20shot%20the%20leopard%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20light%20in%20its%20eyes%20go%20out.%20That%20was%20the%20moment%20he%20was%20converted.%20He%20realised%20it%20was%20a%20dreadful%20thing%20to%20do%3B%20a%20cruel%20sport.%20He%20became%20extremely%20sorrowful%2C%20almost%20like%20an%20epiphany.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20he%20became%20a%20conservationist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20buzzword%20today%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20conservation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewasn%E2%80%99t%20understood%20as%20well%20in%20the%201960s.%20But%20Billy%20Arjan%20led%20the%20revolution%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Tiger%20Haven%E2%80%99%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20present-day%20Dudhwa%20Tiger%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20350px)%20100vw%2C%20350px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billy%20Arjan%20Singh%20had%20a%20fascination%20for%20tigers%20and%20spent%20four%20decades%20ensuring%20they%20were%20well%20protected.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821.jpg%20350w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBilly%20Arjan%20Singh%20had%20a%20fascination%20for%20tigers%20and%20spent%20four%20decades%20ensuring%20they%20were%20well%20protected%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftigerhavensociety.org%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Haven%20Society%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20inception%20of%20Tiger%20Haven%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20how%20the%20summer%20of%201959%20was%20an%20unforgettable%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20out%20into%20the%20forest%20on%20Bhagwan%20Piari%2C%20the%20elephant%20with%20whom%20I%20spent%2025%20wonderful%20years.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20Himalayan%20ranges%20across%20the%20Dudhwa%20grasslands.%20At%20the%20confluence%20of%20the%20Soheli%20and%20Neora%20rivers%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20that%20was%20owned%20by%20a%20politician%20who%20had%20lost%20all%20interest%20in%20it.%20I%20bought%20it%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20functioning%20farm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%2C%20the%20farm%20went%20through%20a%20transmutation%20of%20sorts%20and%20became%20a%20haven%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279646%2Fbest-wildlife-photography-destinations-india-kaziranga-kabini-ranthambore-kaziranga%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20was%20allowed%20to%20thrive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20him%2C%20this%20act%20felt%20like%20%E2%80%9Clike%20repaying%20old%20debts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeconding%20this%20narrative%20of%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20tigers%20is%20Samir%20Sinha%20IFS%2C%20who%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20WWF-India%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20held%20very%20strong%20views%20and%20would%20regularly%20type%20away%20letters%20on%20his%20trusty%20typewriter%20to%20flag%20his%20concerns%20on%20issues%20that%20he%20considered%20important.%20Though%20his%20prolific%20writing%20was%20curtailed%20due%20to%20the%20physical%20effort%20of%20typing%20in%20his%20last%20years%2C%20even%20with%20failing%20health%2C%20his%20eyes%20would%20light%20up%20at%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20tiger%2C%20and%20he%20was%20always%20eager%20to%20engage%20in%20efforts%20in%20support%20of%20this%20majestic%20animal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20years%20succeeding%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20Dudhwa%20where%20he%20began%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiger%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20years%20were%20coloured%20with%20experiments%20and%20accolades%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20through%20waves%20of%20conflict%20posed%20by%20communities%20who%20depended%20on%20the%20game%20and%20stepping%20closer%20to%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Bring%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20the%20conservation%20of%20tigers%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20easy%20until%20he%20had%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops.%20And%20the%20story%20of%20how%20he%20compelled%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20consider%20protecting%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20puts%20this%20never-die-spirit%20into%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrinda%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20duo%20would%20often%20correspond%20with%20each%20other%20through%20postcards.%20She%20then%20proceeds%20to%20read%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Duff%20Hart-Davis%E2%80%99%20biography%2C%20wh